        "subject": "LU-0000 tests: perform failover test on ZFS",
        "message": "LU-0000 tests: perform failover test on ZFS\n\nThis is for test only.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly \\\nenvdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes,REQFAIL=100,DURATION=28800 \\\nmdtfilesystemtype=zfs mdsfilesystemtype=zfs ostfilesystemtype=zfs \\\nclientdistro=el6 ossdistro=el6 mdsdistro=el6 clientarch=x86_64 \\\nossarch=x86_64 mdsarch=x86_64 \\\nclientcount=4 osscount=2 mdscount=2 \\\nmdssizegb=10 ostsizegb=10 \\\nausteroptions=-R failover=true iscsi=1 \\\ntestlist=recovery-small,replay-ost-single,replay-dual\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I155a59d2f4b7a1909d8a9979d0a6c09238b3b114\n"
      },
